            "title": "觀音借庫｜紅磡觀音廟善信絡繹不絕 祈求新一年財運亨通",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"觀音借庫｜紅磡觀音廟善信絡繹不絕 祈求新一年財運亨通\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/f9c6ae02bb5ac70be0cb2d777e1af3a2/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250222/_2025022223521194224.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">觀音借庫｜紅磡觀音廟善信絡繹不絕 祈求新一年財運亨通</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>周日（2月23日）是農曆正月廿六，傳統上是觀音開庫的日子。周六（2月22日）晚上10時許，紅磡觀音廟外已有過百善信到場，在佛光街遊樂場排隊，等候入廟參拜祈福。至晚上11時子時觀音廟開門，善信入廟祈福，紛紛借「一億八千萬」、「三億八千萬」，以祈求新一年財運亨通、平安順遂。另外，廟外香燭店舖亦忙於售賣借庫所需祭品，顧客絡繹不絕。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4097606/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"正月廿六觀音開庫，市民入紅磡觀音廟祈福。尹敬堂攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d3596c58be7c1bd155a8db3568e238ae/2025-02/KakaoTalk_20250222_232448518_08.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        正月廿六觀音開庫，市民入紅磡觀音廟祈福。尹敬堂攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4097608/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"善信手執清香入廟。尹敬堂攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/115fc03f345728c51bb3cec229ad47af/2025-02/KakaoTalk_20250222_232448518_01.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        善信手執清香入廟。尹敬堂攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4097607/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"善信紛紛借「一億八千萬」、「三億八千萬」，以祈求新一年財運亨通。尹敬堂攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/fccb7fcc2bc6d8b6f96b7fc7d64c4213/2025-02/KakaoTalk_20250222_232448518_06.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        善信紛紛借「一億八千萬」、「三億八千萬」，以祈求新一年財運亨通。尹敬堂攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4097605/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/7464d12840a4883e37980277d1b173c0/2025-02/KakaoTalk_20250222_232448518_07.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4097602/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"過百市民在佛光街遊樂場排隊。尹敬堂攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/73f2f6bee4c8333e793b09de3204ccc0/2025-02/KakaoTalk_20250222_223337656.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        過百市民在佛光街遊樂場排隊。尹敬堂攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4097601/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"警員在場維持秩序。尹敬堂攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/30100b244cd9ab4ea9f77504fcf5340b/2025-02/KakaoTalk_20250222_223337656_03.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        警員在場維持秩序。尹敬堂攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4097600/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/1f6894e3423ee31ef0185cdb64919593/2025-02/KakaoTalk_20250222_223337656_04.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4097596/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"廟外香燭店舖亦忙於售賣借庫所需祭品。尹敬堂攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a8e4b37b59c2ce5f1c8c53139160907d/2025-02/KakaoTalk_20250222_223337656_10.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        廟外香燭店舖亦忙於售賣借庫所需祭品。尹敬堂攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4097597/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"顧客絡繹不絕。尹敬堂攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/5a79d08e3d9fe0259c8b04532f2bbbfe/2025-02/KakaoTalk_20250222_223337656_08.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        顧客絡繹不絕。尹敬堂攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4097598/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a6cae6f935bb82576584a5a1eae00c17/2025-02/KakaoTalk_20250222_223337656_07.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>因應排隊人流眾多，警方設置鐵馬，並派員控制人流秩序，以及於紅磡機利士南路考評局門外設置「關愛區」，安排70歲或以上、行動不便、孕婦或持有「殘疾人士登記證」人士，於「關愛區」內輪候。\n\n</p><h2>觀音借庫善信限帶3枝細香</h2>\n<p>除紅磡觀音廟之外，銅鑼灣大坑蓮花宮及筲箕灣天后古廟，亦已實施特別開放時間，以方便公眾人士前往上述廟宇參神及借庫。華人廟宇委員會提醒善信，只限攜帶3枝細香入廟，紅磡觀音廟及銅鑼灣大坑蓮花宮的點香區均設於廟外，所有參拜善信必須在廟外指定的點香區內點香，廟宇範圍內亦禁止燃點任何蠟燭及燃燒衣寶。\n\n</p>\n<p><strong>相關報道：<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/lifetips/3428855\">觀音借庫攻略2025 | 正月廿六觀音借庫 全港12大熱門借庫廟宇一覽 附借庫／還庫／開庫日／流程一文看清！</a></strong>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2054356/即時-港聞-觀音借庫-紅磡觀音廟善信絡繹不絕-祈求新一年財運亨通",
            "pub_date": "2025-02-23 00:01:43",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "日拉麵店不滿食客負評 PO相公審威脅「處刑」遭網友撻伐",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/7c395c666510b1cfc776566964f0ad1c/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250222/_2025022223355118824.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\"></figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>日本京都一間名叫「TOYOJIRO」（とよ二郎）的拉麵店，因不滿顧客用餐後給予負評，竟然在社群媒體上公開顧客照片，甚至懸賞10萬日圓（約5200港元）徵求該顧客的詳細資訊，還揚言處決顧客，極端行徑引發熱議。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"店家人肉搜索誓言找出給負評的客人「報復」。 X\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/c9a017157722aa3cd6c9149aab9b43ff/2025-02/GkIaf6pbQAAtUcX.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        店家人肉搜索誓言找出給負評的客人「報復」。 X\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>該拉麵自詡為京都高評價拉麵店，卻因一則顧客批評服務不佳的負評而惱怒，竟公開顧客用餐時的照片，還懸賞起底，威脅找到人後要痛打一頓。\n\n</p>\n<p>不僅如此，店家還在文中狂罵該顧客「程度低」、「傻子」，並警告這種人「最好別外出用餐」、「有種就再來店裡，我一定親自『款待』，可不會手下留情！」\n\n</p>\n<p><strong>相關新聞：<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/realtime-world/3358798/\">人氣拉麵店武道家禁邊食邊玩電話再禁耳機 老闆轟出餐也聽不到</a></strong>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"店家懸賞尋人要求再吃一次然後貼圖給好評「不會讓其家人安全」。 X\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/3426e071166502f22a4442c97dace21a/2025-02/GkIaffhaAAIaPa0.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        店家懸賞尋人要求再吃一次然後貼圖給好評「不會讓其家人安全」。 X\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>日本網紅「コレコレ@超配信者」在X上揭露此事，貼文瀏覽次數突破3500萬次。網友到該店的Google評論灌入大量一星負評，雖然目前回升至4.7顆星，但評論總數僅71則，其Instagram帳號也關閉留言功能。\n\n</p>\n<p>目前，TOYOJIRO拉麵尚未對外正式回應此事件。\n\n</p>\n<p><strong>相關新聞：<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/china-taiwan/3359238/\">台中無人拉麵店Po相公審客人捱告 霸氣老闆娘別挑戰底線 </a></strong>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2054355/即時-國際-日拉麵店不滿食客負評-PO相公審威脅-處刑-遭網友撻伐",
            "pub_date": "2025-02-22 23:41:14",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "全運男子手球測試賽│港隊挫澳門與江蘇爭王座",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/311f286621ea9d151b2f92d552199995/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250222/_2025022223271040348.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\"></figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>港隊在昨日的全運男子手球測試賽以33:19挫澳門，今日將於決賽與擊敗廣東隊的江蘇爭冠軍。港隊隊長謝永輝表示啟德體藝館要算是他比賽過的場館中最好的1個。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"港隊陳浩諺（左）趁門龍門出迎下手射入。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/5aea1e13b4fc61559c8cbc0ab033ea3b/2025-02/174023759255620.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        港隊陳浩諺（左）趁門龍門出迎下手射入。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>全場佔盡上風的港隊半場已領先18:9，但下半場竟頭9分鐘未有斬獲，被澳門追至只有4分差距，但隨後透過換人及打快攻後再進一步拋離對手致勝。而關鍵時刻被換入的陳浩諺連入4球穩定大勢，他亦榮膺今仗MVP。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"擬進攻的港隊隊長謝永輝（中）遭澳門隊雙人攔截。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/371269ec069441a84d3cc44f34cbe97d/2025-02/174023764589586.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        擬進攻的港隊隊長謝永輝（中）遭澳門隊雙人攔截。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>陳浩諺說：「場地是我比賽過數一數二的好，除了新和大外，最開心是看見那麼多香港球迷到來打氣，氣氛的熱鬧是我們從未感受過的，至於全運會，我們希望在香港球迷面前可取得獎牌。」\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"港隊簡翊文飛身射門。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/75bc78b72d03ff79bac1056e8a6802dc/2025-02/174023769572375.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        港隊簡翊文飛身射門。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>陳浩諺膺今仗MVP\n\n</p>\n<p>至於在隊內已逾10年的謝永輝更表示，腦海中暫難有其他場地比啟德這場館更好：「亞洲的場多為固定的手球場，多數都很舊和空間不大，只有歐洲場如啟德一展是可改變的多用途場地，但都未及啟德氣氛好，我們未試過主場而且聽見那麼多球迷叫喊和唱歌為我們打氣，真的立即精神為之一振。」\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"港隊球迷帶同橫額到場打氣。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e927d1b9c08fd9732324b0de4f12baf1/2025-02/174023775764539.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        港隊球迷帶同橫額到場打氣。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>謝永輝說：「明日決賽鬥全國冠軍江蘇，我們撇開勝負，只希望把備戰和所練習的都發揮出來，去年我們也曾跟江蘇一同練習，知道彼此的實力。至於全運會，我也明白我們是列於全國實力只列第6、7位，因為北京、上海、安徽及山東等隊伍實力都強，但仍希望藉後這大半年再練好和再能在這個場練習。」江蘇在另1場比賽以29:23勝廣東入決賽，落敗的廣東則與澳門在季軍戰中相遇。 攝影、記者:陸永鴻\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"江蘇球員力阻廣東隊攻門。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/470cd6d1f7d3b1d992a2af2ebc865515/2025-02/174023784287219.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        江蘇球員力阻廣東隊攻門。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p> \n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"全國運動會統籌辦公室主任楊德強到場視察。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/fdac4c900b457b0e7fe30e900b3696e3/2025-02/174023790193162.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        全國運動會統籌辦公室主任楊德強到場視察。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"江蘇門將王權出迎時被皮球擊中即時爆缸。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/1450ab8cc63932632667ce2838829a26/2025-02/174023795215926.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        江蘇門將王權出迎時被皮球擊中即時爆缸。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p> \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2054354/即時-體育-全運男子手球測試賽│港隊挫澳門與江蘇爭王座",
            "pub_date": "2025-02-22 23:36:15",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "難民罪犯在英國說謊即可逃避遣返? 「不愛吃外國雞塊」竟過關",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"難民在歐洲各國都是棘手問題。 美聯社\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/53bd4943e518a1fe122843cfbe327018/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250222/_2025022223022875387.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">難民在歐洲各國都是棘手問題。 美聯社</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>英國受移民問題困擾，近年收緊移民政策。英國《每日電訊報》研究了一些法庭案例，發現部分人不被遣返的理由匪夷所思，其中一名外籍罪犯竟說「兒子不喜歡外國雞塊」就被允許繼續留在英國；還有非法移民獲法官裁定不用驅逐，理由是「他已在英國待了這麼久」。即使移民者對驅逐命令提出異議時說謊或給出「不可信」的證據，移民法官仍依據「歐洲人權公約」（ECHR）授予其留在英國的權利。\n\n</p><h2>家鄉無親戚也是理由？</h2>\n<p>報道提出一些例子，一名54歲的津巴布韋婦女在申請庇護中說謊被定罪，面臨遣返。她編造了一個博客批評津巴布韋政權，進而主張若被遣返會遭到迫害，結果對遣返令提出上訴獲批。還有另一名非法移民謊稱在家鄉斯里蘭卡沒有什麼親戚，主張若被遣返，會違反「歐洲人權公約」中保障的家庭生活權。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"英國收緊移民政策。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d349fdfe3f908655bae04aabc37dcd2a/2023-12/11_6_0.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        英國收緊移民政策。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"英倫海峽偷渡潮的問題令英國相當頭痛。 路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/981fdc556642af572cf518a547740eeb/2025-02/2024-09-04T170937Z_1060854881_RC2KT9AJ0YAL_RTRMADP_3_EUROPE-MIGRANTS-FRANCE.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        英倫海峽偷渡潮的問題令英國相當頭痛。 路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"英倫海峽偷渡潮的問題令英國相當頭痛。 路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/2588b4cd3f6a5adc60fcd6d29e699fd0/2025-02/2025-01-01T171240Z_1539923212_RC2E99APFYAJ_RTRMADP_3_MIGRATION-BRITAIN.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        英倫海峽偷渡潮的問題令英國相當頭痛。 路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"英國邊境部隊人員護送未成年人到倫敦南部克羅伊登的移民中心。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/595d586341ac2b86eacbcaa0d53faf78/2025-02/LON102_EUROPE-MIGRANTS-CHILDREN_1018_11.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        英國邊境部隊人員護送未成年人到倫敦南部克羅伊登的移民中心。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"英國邊境部隊人員護送未成年人到倫敦南部克羅伊登的移民中心。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/2cd2d3560c76e4c3d0dffe3fdca610b0/2025-02/LON115_EUROPE-MIGRANTS-CHILDREN_1017_11.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        英國邊境部隊人員護送未成年人到倫敦南部克羅伊登的移民中心。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"英國邊境部隊人員護送未成年人到倫敦南部克羅伊登的移民中心。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ea8811b5bf3274bab8eedfe9a3a708dc/2025-02/LON127_EUROPE-MIGRANTS-CHILDREN_1017_11.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        英國邊境部隊人員護送未成年人到倫敦南部克羅伊登的移民中心。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>在其中一宗上訴案中，法官們還引用過去見解，認為即使上訴人說謊，法庭也應該小心「不要輕易駁回其上訴」—法官不應太快因為上訴人曾在某些事情上說謊，就得到他在其他方面的主張都不可信的結論。\n\n</p>\n<p>另外，有阿爾巴尼亞罪犯主張兒子「厭惡外國雞塊」後，竟也能逃離被遣返的命運。還有曾性侵幼童的巴基斯坦戀童癖罪犯，因為遣返會「對他自己的小孩過於不利」而不用遣返。\n\n</p>\n<p>英國影子內政大臣范翹思（Chris Philp）表示，這些極度不堪一擊的主張太常被接受，或採取了定義過於寬廣的「歐洲人權公約」規定。他直言，難怪在歐洲的非法移民都想搭乘小船跨過海峽，「他們知道我們的體系太軟弱了，這必須被劃下句點」。他認為，有關庇護或人權的主張應該只能被提出一次，而那些在法庭上說謊的非法移民就該被驅逐。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
